    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>Drive Thru Simulator: Prologue</strong> 给你提供完整体验的前瞻，您将在其中接受订单、烹饪美味餐点、管理库存并发展您的餐厅。掌握速度、效率和客户满意度的艺术，将一个小小的路边摊变成终极快餐帝国！ <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/412e1297fba0e44aa9534758b1ed6d40.poster.avif?t=1751357917\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/412e1297fba0e44aa9534758b1ed6d40.webm?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/412e1297fba0e44aa9534758b1ed6d40.mp4?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍟<strong> 主要特点：</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在线购物时间！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >订购您需要的一切，确保您的餐厅顺利运营！新鲜的食材、必需的用品和厨房升级——一切都直接送到您家门口。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/5ec009d540dc8a90c110d7e472cc929e.poster.avif?t=1751357917\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/5ec009d540dc8a90c110d7e472cc929e.webm?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/5ec009d540dc8a90c110d7e472cc929e.mp4?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快速配送，新鲜食材！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持高质量的农产品、肉类和必需品的库存。良好的库存管理意味着更满意的顾客和更快速的服务！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/d1a9331b9951bc39e28f0f52b103c278.poster.avif?t=1751357917\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/d1a9331b9951bc39e28f0f52b103c278.webm?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/d1a9331b9951bc39e28f0f52b103c278.mp4?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>补充库存与整理！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过正确安排食材来高效管理存储空间。保持厨房充足的库存，避免在高峰时段缺少关键物品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/d49c6e20b225b4162d5f78c3ec2a3bd8.poster.avif?t=1751357917\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/d49c6e20b225b4162d5f78c3ec2a3bd8.webm?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/d49c6e20b225b4162d5f78c3ec2a3bd8.mp4?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>随意摆放！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义您的餐厅布局！根据您的需求，精准地安置烹饪站、准备区域和储藏区，确保工作流的最高效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/8e23387cd8e700174a15ac29e0337da9.poster.avif?t=1751357917\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/8e23387cd8e700174a15ac29e0337da9.webm?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/8e23387cd8e700174a15ac29e0337da9.mp4?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为烤炉大师！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >烤制多汁的汉堡，炸出脆皮薯条，精确地烹饪美味的餐点。完美您的烹饪技巧，提供城里最好的快餐！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/1c6035fec18d66609852833e94695749.poster.avif?t=1751357917\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/1c6035fec18d66609852833e94695749.webm?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062050/extras/1c6035fec18d66609852833e94695749.mp4?t=1751357917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>清洁时间！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持厨房和就餐区一尘不染，以确保获得最高的卫生评级。干净的餐厅意味着更好的评论和更满意的顾客！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>演示版与序章的区别：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UI 升级</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>改进的教程</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>日夜系统</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>烤炉改进</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拖把机制</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扑克小游戏</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心机制</strong>    </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入您的愿望单！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drive Thru Simulator: Prologue</strong> 是 <strong>免费</strong> 的！每一个决定都将塑造您快餐帝国的未来。您能保持队伍流动，满足挑剔的顾客，并掌握效率的艺术吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>立即将其加入您的愿望单！</strong></p>",
